name: Parkover - Car Parking App
description:
Hello,


Parkover - App to Book Parking slot

This slot booking app will help you to find the best parking slots close to your chosen destination. Pay only for the time your car was parked when you checkout. The app also uses AR technology to guide you towards the slot where you parked your car when you return from your errand. Let parkover do the job of finding the most suitable parking location for you and never be late for any of your appointments.
